7. THE FUTURE

We know that this won't change the world, but maybe some 
other people start to think and recognize that we can 
only change the world together. We need a world, where
everyone can live without being afraid of their opinion,
their nationality or their skin.


8. DISKMAGAZINE

If we get many responses, we will start with a disk-
magazine, that will report about news from all over the 
world. So write!
